  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nThis is from a heap snapshot I used to sync Pyrmont\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1133\" alt=\"retained_BeaconStateContext\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/10568965/111410741-e289be00-870b-11eb-92aa-81099b09b8e8.png\">\r\n\r\nThe promise being retained is the one in processChainSegment https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/master/packages/lodestar/src/chain/blocks/process.ts#L141\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nThe promise and BeaconStateContext instance are both not retained in memory\r\n\r\n**Steps to Reproduce**\r\n+ Sync Pyrmont\r\n+ The more `await sleep(0);`  calls we add to `stateTransition` function, the more Promises are retained. \r\n\r\n**Desktop (please complete the following information):**\r\n- Commit hash: a855a08\r\n",
